<plot>Three friends that work together at a Hong Kong business firm put in overtime one night and, while at the office, stumbled upon a bag filled with 10 million dollars in cash. Ecstatic with their wealthy find, they took the money and began to concoct a perfect and safe date and time to start spending it. However, when it became known that the business firm's senior manager was blackmailed and the money intended for the blackmailer was reported missing, the friends fear that they might be reprimanded for finding and taking the cash.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?123497</url></doc>
